      "description": "The Oracle WebLogic Server component of Oracle Fusion Middleware (subcomponent - WLS Security) is susceptible to remote command execution. Supported versions that are affected are 10.3.6.0.0, 12.1.3.0.0, 12.2.1.1.0 and 12.2.1.2.0. This easily exploitable vulnerability allows unauthenticated attackers with network access via T3 to compromise Oracle WebLogic Server.\n",
